.6. More Bash options

.6.1. Displaying options

to display all shell options:
	set -o

.6.2. Changing options 

options can be set when calling the shell, during shell operations or included in shell config files.
to change the current enviroment temporarily use	
	set -o OPTION	for enabling
	set +o OPTION	for disabling

